        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: In figures 4 and 6, the authors use immunogold electron microscopy to localize CALM in rat synapses. Figure 4 is synapses from CA1 neurons and figure 6 is synapses from cerebellar granule cells on Purkinje neurons.. Experimental description: From results, \"Two rats were processed for postembedding immunogold labelling...\"" ;
